// Context Handling Essentials (see README.md for more details):
//
// The key checks the active window for a Find Results buffer.
//
// Key:       is_find_results_buffer_open
// Operator:  equal or not_equal (ST defaults to: equal)
// Operand:   true or false (ST defaults to: true)
